28 3. The department of elementary and secondary
29 education shall develop guidelines suitable for training or
30 professional development in youth suicide awareness and
31 prevention. The department may develop materials that may
32 be used for the training described under subsection 2 of
33 this section or may offer districts materials developed by a
34 third party that districts may use for the training.
35 4. For the 2028-29 school year and all subsequent
36 school years, suicide prevention training described in
37 subdivisions (2) and (3) of subsection 2 of this section and
38 guidelines and materials developed or used under subsection
